{"tid":1578873,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"「中國知道我會贏」 特朗普：中美或美國總統大選前達協議","createTime":"2019-09-18T10:13:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-18T10:56:15.000Z","uid":68738,"like":9,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"366da2c8495871ac379c97e37281b747433dcde0","tid":1578873,"uid":68738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T10:13:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static01.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2450000/2453986/20190918_win_v1_600.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic01.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2450000%2F2453986%2F20190918_win_v1_600.png&h=f96b3565&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n中美官員準備周四會面，為10月中美貿易戰新一輪談判鋪路之際，美國總統特朗普再次釋出談判訊號。特朗普稱，中美貿易戰有可能在明年11月美國總統大選之前達成協議。特朗普又指中國知道他會順利連任，假如往後再談，中方獲得的待遇會差得多。<br />\n<br />\n美國大選會於2020年11月3日舉行，特朗普正在遊走美國各地為競選連任造勢，他周二在空軍一號專機上向傳媒表示，中美貿易戰可能在大選前後達成協議：<br />\n<br />\n我想不久之後就會達成協議，可能在大選之前，或者在大選後一天。假如是大選之後，這會是你們從未見過的協議，會是史上最偉大的協議，中國清楚這一點。<br />\n（I think there'll be a deal maybe soon, maybe before the election, or one day after the election. And if it's after the election, it'll be a deal like you've never seen, it'll be the greatest deal ever and China knows that.）<br />\n<br />\n特朗普聲言，中方情願與另一位美國總統談判，但卻知道他會順利連任：<br />\n<br />\n他們認為我會輕易贏出，並為此感到擔心。我告訴中國：如果選後才達協議，會比現在壞得多。他們是否情願其他人贏？絕對是。<br />\n（China thinks I'm going to win so easily and they're concerned because I told them:&lsquo;If it's after the election, it's going to be far worse than what it is right now.&rsquo;Would they like to see somebody else win? Absolutely.）<br />\n<br />\n特朗普上周在白宮指出，美方正考慮與中國達成臨時協議。外界推斷，臨時協議不會覆蓋知識產權、技術轉讓等經濟模式事宜，只會包括採購農產品和撤銷部分關稅等措施。但美國貿易代表萊特希澤（Robert Lighthizer）據報對臨時協議有保留，主張爭取「真正協議」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://inews.hket.com/article/2453986?r=mcsdfb2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Finews.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2453986%3Fr%3Dmcsdfb2&d=Ii72mHdDrz30Fn2z87Evj0n12mAFq1syGW6OSBl8LUM%3D&h=a8dfbf4f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://inews.hket.com/article/2453986?r=mcsdfb2</a>"},{"pid":"8d213880307d5a80bcd8f4a90a1b1d664a073e45","tid":1578873,"uid":117906,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T10:13:43.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">全球響應「929全球集會抗赤納粹」</span></span></strong><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">全世界一齊對準極權！</span></span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1577380\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1577380</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hWqVmOV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhWqVmOV.jpg&h=075c7745&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/n1tov9s.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fn1tov9s.png&h=0af09f95&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4b36ef49a7aa3edc5b1bb904144faf00fe787a29","tid":1578873,"uid":242537,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T10:13:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/EEt_hKMXYAIDATl?format=jpg&amp;name=medium\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FEEt_hKMXYAIDATl%3Fformat%3Djpg%26name%3Dmedium&h=d4111daf&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0ebce4ca5c0ae7f9e97120a1ca302dd83813b5c5","tid":1578873,"uid":65449,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T10:15:12.000Z","msg":"商界人係唔同啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/wink.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你睇下前一個奧巴馬傻閪閪有份養大中國呢隻老虎<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a6753a5f5a7d9dc0c6df3dcd8f85e96f9420bbd0","tid":1578873,"uid":128100,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T10:15:41.000Z","msg":"又話對支那強硬既...<br />\n<br />\n我睇唔透 有冇高人指點下"},{"pid":"5ba0629a61ee69278338a122ecb8d99ef0e12b50","tid":1578873,"uid":167548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T10:16:18.000Z","msg":"【9.23~9.27】全球「反共」聯軍來了我帶路！快閃式萬國「民主」旗號召世界<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/eccnjS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/eccnjS</a><br />\n<blockquote><br />\n由於香港身為<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>東道主</strong></span></span>倘若因為任何原因而令到遊行人數小得難睇, 是不理想的！<br />\n<br />\n同埋我寧願<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>10.1國殤</strong></span>打到拆天就最好啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />當然大家請記著呢日唔是End-game<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 由美帝反共眾議員可以見到場戰爭並非一朝一夕<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 失去所有勇武運動將難以持續<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n大家講到星期日9.29是全球性<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />, 單靠香港人文宣團隊twitter retweet比當地人是難以收到巨大宣傳效益<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">唯有無比juicy<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />方法去呼喚他國人民, 同埋件事夠juicy<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />外國媒體先會幫你免費頭版</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: brown;\"><strong>【9.23~9.27】全球「反共」聯軍來了我帶路！<br />\n集合時間：1930~2000<br />\n遊行時間：2000~終點和平散去 (預計9點前行到遮打即龍頭散去)<br />\n舉行日期：9月23日至9月27日晚上快閃式遊行<br />\n遊行路線：修頓球場 至 遮打花園<br />\n注意事項：遊行完就即時由中環遮打盡快散去！不起衝突！人小就行行人路<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n衣著：遊行時黑色, 前往及離開時非黑色<br />\n快閃遊行目的：號召全球「反共」聯軍同時響應9.29大遊行, 盡可能與香港同步舉行！</strong></span><br />\n利申：是次遊行屬自發性質, 沒有不反對通知書<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n講到反共你走去申請唔好傻啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我主張每晚均可見到頭60名民主國度<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n只要有60位手足舉60支旗個畫面已經夠晒Juicy<br />\n首先你話該國家一直龜縮有咩撚用,舉嚟把撚啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但是9.29反共大遊行號召目標是各國人民,<br />\n如果我地真是連續一星期舉民主國家國旗, <span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong>當地右翼會相當自豪<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></strong></span>,<br />\n同埋每晚我地可以twitter開放檢討比各國人民知道其國旗在香港揚起以打倒中共</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc389d5d68a236e3a0efd27883a7acabb3686b6b","tid":1578873,"uid":271234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T10:16:58.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">Brexit都係靠呢招食糊！</span><br />\n 【眾籌 Youtube 廣告】 本地文宣 : 多媒體廣告 <a href=\"https://lih.kg/dRrFcS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/dRrFcS</a>"},{"pid":"53ea9b12d5b300c8030c9c9e8b2283f2dc98dae8","tid":1578873,"uid":4258,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0ebce4ca5c0ae7f9e97120a1ca302dd83813b5c5","tid":1578873,"uid":65449,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T10:15:12.000Z","msg":"商界人係唔同啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/wink.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你睇下前一個奧巴馬傻閪閪有份養大中國呢隻老虎<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T10:16:59.000Z","msg":"外界推斷，臨時協議不會覆蓋知識產權、技術轉讓等經濟模式事宜，只會包括採購農產品和撤銷部分關稅等措施。<br />\n<br />\n唔好咁快打飛機住"},{"pid":"634ac785fc4f41417fac316a58ddec29b79e3050","tid":1578873,"uid":167548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a6753a5f5a7d9dc0c6df3dcd8f85e96f9420bbd0","tid":1578873,"uid":128100,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T10:15:41.000Z","msg":"又話對支那強硬既...<br />\n<br />\n我睇唔透 有冇高人指點下"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T10:17:11.000Z","msg":"日日撚狗唔洗理"},{"pid":"8a84235b185ba5d0e58b241bcd02a87e31c69201","tid":1578873,"uid":30006,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"a6753a5f5a7d9dc0c6df3dcd8f85e96f9420bbd0","tid":1578873,"uid":128100,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T10:15:41.000Z","msg":"又話對支那強硬既...<br />\n<br />\n我睇唔透 有冇高人指點下"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T10:17:14.000Z","msg":"達成協議 = 中國玩完"},{"pid":"2509c02